Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.58,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}不期之晨 已不復歸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.50,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所重複者 僅為鮮活明艷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.50,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}汝亦從此 於世再無瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.00,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}黃粱短夢堆重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.01,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}昔日轟華化永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.76,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}唯留謊言難釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.68,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}予此絕世以痛傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.43,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}心若所願則易惘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.48,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}故而切勿遠離吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:37.07,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}令汝所見之明日 吐息煥然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.99,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}張開雙臂歡笑相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.78,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}決計不再分離


