Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:21.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}滿溢之淚 盈眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:26.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何故 每逢抱持守護之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:30.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}心扉閉合心意難猜？
